node.text: Founder of @iamcaribbeing Shelley Worrell (@shelleyworrell) is behind the bar cart showing us how to mix up extra-special cola drinks, featuring @fevertreemixers Cola. Not-Your-Typical Rum and Cola gets its upgrade from a splash of Champagne (see what we mean by extra-special?), while her Whiskey and Cola gets a lift from a dash of bitters and some fresh lime juice. Whichever you choose, each is bound to impress at your next happy hour. #f52partner

node.title: Not-Your-Typical Rum and Cola & Whiskey and Cola with Orange Bitters

node.text: Resident @carolinagelen is back for another episode of Choose Your Own Recipe Adventure and is prepared to tackle your ingredient picks! The results are in, and now Carolina is tasked with developing a flambéed dish using honey, whole milk, citrus, and the wildcard, chile powder. Can she complete this challenge? Watch to find out, then head to the link in bio for the recipe. #f52community

node.title: Choose Your Own Recipe Adventure with Carolina Gelen

node.text: Founder of @iamcaribbeing Shelley Worrell (@shelleyworrell) is behind the bar cart showing us how to mix up extra-special cola drinks, featuring @fevertreemixers Cola. Not-Your-Typical Rum and Cola gets its upgrade from a splash of Champagne (see what we mean by extra-special?), while her Whiskey and Cola gets a lift from a dash of bitters and some fresh lime juice. Whichever you choose, each is bound to impress at your next happy hour. #f52partner

node.text: Step aside regular salads, there's a new salad in town, and it's @thisiskaychun's Grilled Summer Salad With Tonnato Verde! Not only does it use seasonal produce favorites (think: beans, sweet corn, and juicy tomatoes), but it gets dressed in a tonnato verde, complete with capers, anchovies, and soft tofu (to replace mayo).
